snippet.textDisplay: People judge clashes these days purely off kill shots in lyrics as opposed to the old grime clash days when bars, flow, energy and whether you could make the crowd spazz out would determine the winner. Go check out Don’t Flop grime clash videos to see the type of era Wiley is coming from.
